sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Tamu as Tamu Hotel
    participant ChatUI as Chatbot UI<br/>(/chatbot/page.tsx)
    participant ChatAPI as Chat Route<br/>(/api/chat/route.ts)
    participant Gemini as Google Gemini<br/>(gemini-2.5-flash)
    participant Tool as Tool: cekKetersediaan
    participant DB as Supabase PostgreSQL

    Tamu->>ChatUI: "Ada kamar tersedia 15-17 Juli?"
    ChatUI->>ChatAPI: POST /api/chat<br/>{messages: [...]}

    ChatAPI->>Gemini: streamText({model: gemini-2.5-flash,<br/>system: hotelConcierge,<br/>tools: {cekKetersediaan, ...},<br/>messages})

    Gemini->>Gemini: Detect intent: cek ketersediaan<br/>Extract: checkIn=2024-07-15,<br/>checkOut=2024-07-17

    Gemini->>Tool: invoke cekKetersediaan({<br/>checkIn, checkOut, tipeKamar?<br/>})

    Tool->>DB: SELECT room_id FROM reservations<br/>WHERE status NOT IN ('cancelled','no_show')<br/>AND check_in < checkOut<br/>AND check_out > checkIn
    DB-->>Tool: busyBookings (room_id list)

    Tool->>Tool: busyRoomIds = bookings.map(b => b.room_id)

    Tool->>DB: SELECT id, number, type, base_price<br/>FROM rooms<br/>WHERE status = 'available'<br/>AND id NOT IN (busyRoomIds)<br/>[AND type ILIKE %tipeKamar%]
    DB-->>Tool: availableRooms

    alt availableRooms kosong
        Tool-->>Gemini: { status: 'unavailable',<br/>message: 'Tidak ada kamar...' }
    else Ada kamar tersedia
        Tool-->>Gemini: { status: 'available',<br/>rooms: [{id, number, type, base_price}, ...] }
    end

    Gemini->>Gemini: Generate response text +<br/>append ROOM_CARDS_JSON marker

    Gemini-->>ChatAPI: stream chunks (SSE)
    ChatAPI-->>ChatUI: stream response<br/>(useChat hook)

    ChatUI->>ChatUI: Parse ROOM_CARDS_JSON marker<br/>render <RoomCard /> components

    ChatUI-->>Tamu: Tampilkan teks respons +<br/>kartu kamar interaktif

    Note over Tool,DB: Real-time query ke Supabase<br/>memastikan availability akurat<br/>tanpa caching
